LiFePO4 12V 100Ah Lithium Battery 100A BMS Solar Off-grid Trolling Motor Boat RV
Product description:

Lithium iron phosphate batteries are a mature alternative to lead batteries and have all the advantages of lithium iron phosphate technology. The storage system has been specially developed to fully meet today's high demands on batteries and can offer maximum safety and long-term availability even with regular deep discharge. This technology can achieve an extremely long service life, making these batteries ideal traction batteries, and it can also significantly reduce weight, enormous energy reserves and stable voltage even under extreme loads.
 [Smaller and lighter]
The weight of lithium batteries is 1/3 of the weight of lead-acid batteries, which is easy to carry and install, and is an ideal choice for outdoor camping and indoor installation.

[BMS protection]
TCBWORTHY battery has an integrated BMS (battery management system), low self-discharge, can prevent overcharge, deep discharge, overcurrent, overload, short circuit, self-balancing of cell voltage, high temperature discharge cut off，charge protection at low temperature

[Wide application]
The LiFePo4 lithium battery is safe, efficient and portable, suitable for camping, RVs, caravans, electric boats, golf carts, tool trailers, solar panels, children's vehicles or can be used as a backup power supply.
